         <abstract>
            <p>We provide sets of parameters for multiplicative linear congruential generators (MLCGs) of different sizes and good performance with respect to the spectral test. For ℓ = 8,9,..., 64, 127, 128, we take as a modulus m the largest prime smaller than 2&lt;sup&gt;ℓ&lt;/sup&gt;, and provide a list of multipliers a such that the MLCG with modulus m and multiplier a has a good lattice structure in dimensions 2 to 32. We provide similar lists for power-of-two moduli m = 2&lt;sup&gt;ℓ&lt;/sup&gt;, for multiplicative and non-multiplicative LCGs.</p>
          </abstract>
